= Acknowledgement

This report documents the design, implementation, and testing of the *SAP Bug Tracking Management System* — project code *ZBUG_WS* — developed on SAP S40 (Client 324) using ABAP 7.70.

The team acknowledges the opportunity to work on a real-world enterprise system using professional SAP development tools: SE11, SE38, SE51, SE41, SE80, SE93, SMARTFORMS, and SCOT.

The project delivered a full-featured, role-based bug tracking system built as a Module Pool (Type M) ABAP program — surpassing the reference system (`ZPG_BUGTRACKING_*`) in architecture, automation, auditability, and UI quality across 6 development phases (A through F).
